13154.post_excerpt: The Handyman Layout Pack is perfect for small businesses that want to set up a website that matches the industry they're in. The 7 included layouts are solution-oriented and focus on offering visitors a quick and pleasant experience on your website. With both a service and services layout within reach, you can entirely focus on the services you offer.
